data.description: Nestled in the tranquil neighborhood of Elmhurst Estates, this meticulously updated property offers a blend of comfort and versatility that is sure to capture your heart. Step inside to discover a recently updated primary bathroom and an upstairs bathroom, providing modern convenience and style. The renewed rear patio and custom concrete walkways beckon you to enjoy outdoor gatherings and relaxation. A finished basement, complete with its own separate access and exit, opens up a world of possibilities. Whether you envision it as a live-in second quarters, an in-law suite, a rental opportunity, or even an Airbnb, this space adapts to your needs. The property also boasts a storage building and a detached 2-car garage workshop with a full bathroom and loft upstairs, ideal for guest accommodations or additional living quarters. If you're searching for a spacious and flexible living space, look no further. Back on market please see agent only remarks for more information.
